title: Samsung Refrigerator Ice Maker Assembly

installationInstructions.author: larry from RICHLAND, WA
installationInstructions.title: Ice maker freezing over, causing ice to get stuck
installationInstructions.content: Replaced parts, as ordered - very simple. Watched the video before hand. Found that existing assembly did not have the "Y" clip installed. Been making ice for three weeks with no freezing up (yet) - time will tell.
